Catalyst 5: COVID

Following the downgrade, SL’s tourism industry tanked during COVID.

Tourism was one of the largest sources of forex for SL.

Hence, it was another reason why the government needed to use its forex reserves to:

1. Repay debt, &
2. Pay for imports (e.g. fuel)
